  - q: "Can I have a mirror in the bedroom?"
    a: "Mirrors in the bedroom are one of the most debated feng shui topics. Classical feng shui advises against mirrors directly facing the bed, as they can disturb sleep by reflecting energy back and forth. A mirror on a side wall or inside a wardrobe door is generally acceptable. If you have a mirror facing the bed and sleep well, the practical effect on you may be minimal."
  - q: "What is the best bedroom colour for feng shui?"
